{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they knew my father well because he had served in-- in the First World War, and they had a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- but then, slowly but surely, I guess some of them started to distance themselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I don't think the-- the town-- the people that lived there for a while in the town, [? well, ?] they were not active in-- in-- in any of the early incidents, at least.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I know that, later on, it got worse, you know, but at the beginning, I guess, friendship from way past still meant something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Even ?] I remember that when-- one day when I went for a walk with my grandfather, some so-called friends of his were no better.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They started calling-- calling him dirty Jew and-- and-- and all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And these were people who we had known for many years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was frightened, you know, because, I think, my grandfather was in shock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't-- of all people, didn't expect it from them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he-- we were sitting on a bench, so we got up and we left and went back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in general, you know, when you're-- I was four or five years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't-- you remember only sort of outstanding incidents, you know, things which sort of left-- like-- like I said, when they were sitting in the trench, and they started to throw sand on me.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That I remember because it was frightening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we also remember most of the time, going to the orphanage for anything-- you know, any social, whatever you want to call it, life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, Kristallnacht was, of course, an event which I was six and a half at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's November 9-- 10, 1938.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can't forget.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
